        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " but these works must spring out of a root of faith, without which it is impossible to please God. He shall reward him, by a reward of grace, not of debt, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
