        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The reason given why the higher life—the soul—is of priceless value: (1) The Judge is at hand who will condemn self-indulgence and all the works of the lower life, and will reward those who have denied themselves. (2) Further (",
